{"tid":2362376,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拼多多員工連環喪命 工程師跳樓輕生","createTime":"2021-01-11T11:40:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T11:45:05.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6c4bab7aad6fb45f4d38d22867fc43145f5ff92","tid":2362376,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:40:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210111/5POZ3IQNONGRRGPBLJHRY22PWM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210111%2F5POZ3IQNONGRRGPBLJHRY22PWM%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BbScfX6drAaaDYLMstvIIS4%3D&h=a0c44cf8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210111%2F5POZ3IQNONGRRGPBLJHRY22PWM%2F&h=d61136c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210111/5POZ3IQNONGRRGPBLJHRY22PWM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n拼多多員工連環喪命 工程師跳樓輕生<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/RQgYvmTjPf8ngswZk5InmOmvb3c=/4490x2523/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4UZMD6HQGZDCJCFWCYEYKOR43A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FRQgYvmTjPf8ngswZk5InmOmvb3c%3D%2F4490x2523%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4UZMD6HQGZDCJCFWCYEYKOR43A.jpg&h=26e25028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n內地電商巨頭拼多多（圖）近日風波不斷，繼早前一名年輕員工於下班後猝死，前日一名年約23歲的譚姓男員工身穿睡衣睡褲，在長沙家中跳樓自殺，公司對其離世稱致深切哀悼，並表示全力配合善後工作。<br />\n<br />\n據死者父親表示，上周五下午於長沙機場接孩子回家，次日中午12時30分左右，孩子於長沙27樓家中跳樓，當場離世，法醫到場勘驗後確認自殺。據悉，譚男已經通過試用期，並於去年12月30日完成正式聘請流程，其績效平均分數約80分（100分制）。譚男在事發前已購買本月9日下午返回上海的機票。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n22歲女員工疑過勞猝死<br />\n<br />\n禍不單行，較早前一名女員工在去年12月29日凌晨1時30分下班途中突然暈倒，經搶救無效後去世，年僅22歲，生前。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n網易"},{"pid":"c46298e83cbcdc27434bf11b49250e197f9c0964","tid":2362376,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:42:0